readable.content: A baby girl has the contents of a red pot all over her face . A baby girl holding a red plastic box in one hand and eating from it with the other , some of it on her face . A little girl in a highchair has food all over her lower face and her finger in her mouth . A toddler with pudding all over her face and hands from eating with her fingers . The little girl is in her high chair eating jello .
